OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fpatchy light rain which may linger in
OL,7,Fthe east. The best of the drier and
OL,8,Fbrighter conditions will be in west
OL,9,Fwith some afternoon sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FPartly cloudy this evening
OL,12,Fand dry for most, however a few
OL,13,Flingering showers will gradually clear
OL,14,Faway to leave the rest of the night
OL,15,Fdry with clear spells.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA dry, bright morning with
OL,18,Fhazy sunny spells. More in the way of
OL,19,Fcloud in the afternoon and few
OL,20,Fshowers, one or two of these on the
OL,21,Fheavy side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
